title: Shadows Fall The Art of Touring Video DVDRip 2005 with Bonus CD
description:
Follow Shadows Fall around on their tours.  it's not for everyone this type of trashing gurgle singing metal but it certainly has its place in the world.  A VA bonus music folder is included since it was part of the DVD set.
